result.title: Just Do It.
result.content: Do it Just do it **** Don't let your dreams be dreams Yesterday you said tomorrow So just do it Make your dreams come true Just do it **** Some people dream of success While you're gonna wake up and work hard at it Nothing is impossible **** You should get to the point Where anyone else would quit And you're not going to stop there No, what are you waiting for? **** Do it Just do it Yes you can Just do it If you're tired of starting over Stop giving up
